asting: Prophets ordered to delay morning meal, hasten to break fast","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, we company of prophets have been commanded to delay our pre-fasting meal, to hasten to break our fast, and to place our rights hands over our left hands in prayer.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 1770\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14885,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/10\/come-to-blessed-suhur\/","url_meta":{"origin":3769,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Come to the blessed pre-fasting meal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 10, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-'Irbad ibn Sariyah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, invited me to the pre-fasting meal\u00a0during Ramadan and he said, \u201cOnward to the blessed meal!\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2344 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u0650\u0631\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0627\u0636\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0633\u064e\u0627\u0631\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u062f\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650\u064a \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14887,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/10\/must-eat-suhoor\/","url_meta":{"origin":3769,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Suhur: Eat the blessed pre-fasting meal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 10, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Miqdam ibn Ma\u2019dikarib reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYou must take the pre-fasting meal, for it is a blessed meal.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 2164 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0642\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0639\u0652\u062f\u0650\u064a\u0643\u064e\u0631\u0650\u0628\u064e\u00a0\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0643\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0628\u0650\u063a\u064e\u062f\u064e\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0651\u064f\u062d\u064f\u0648\u0631\u0650 \u0641\u064e\u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0647\u064f\u0648\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39756,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/18\/angels-suhoor\/","url_meta":{"origin":3769,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Suhur: Allah and angels bless the pre-fasting meal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 18, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah and His angels send blessings upon those who eat before fasting.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 3467 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15014,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/14\/suhoor-blessed-sip\/","url_meta":{"origin":3769,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Suhur: Angels bless those who eat pre-fasting meal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 14, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe pre-fasting meal is a blessed meal, so do not abandon it even if you only take a sip of water. Verily, Allah and His angels send blessings upon those who take the pre-fasting meal.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14882,"url":"htt